caption: I go to this chipotle every single day for lunch, M-F. My order is the exact same every single time. Today, there was an up charge and when I questioned it, I got charged for a side because I asked for extra cheese on my bowl. It’s absolutely absurd to be charged for extra cheese or anything extra that doesn’t pertain to meat.

Checked out Pancho Villa today during lunch with my coworker. Really pleased! I recently moved here from Chicago, IL & honestly have not been super impressed with the burrito options in SF, but I was proved wrong today! Got the super burrito with chicken & it was ON POINT. Not all tortilla, plenty of filling, good tortilla temp & it didn't tear, chicken was moist, YES! Also, the salsa bar there is winning. Carrots/jalapeños, wide salsa selection & other fixings. But, what really won me over was the service. Amazing! Everyone was friendly, smiling, helpful and the food was great. Will be back! Highly recommend!
